{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-archived-blog-template-js","path":"/2017/05/autonews-with-nlp-feature/","result":{"data":{"archivedBlogPostJson":{"categories":[{"path":"/category/front-end/","name":"前端"},{"path":"/category/pcandinternet/","name":"计算机与网络"}],"tags":[{"name":"人工智能","path":"/tag/ai/"},{"name":"新闻源监控","path":"/tag/auto-news/"},{"name":"机器学习","path":"/tag/machine-learning/"},{"name":"爬虫","path":"/tag/reptile/"},{"name":"算法","path":"/tag/algorithm/"},{"name":"自然语言处理","path":"/tag/nlp/"}],"featured_media":{"childImageSharp":{"gatsbyImageData":{"layout":"fixed","placeholder":{"fallback":"data:image/jpeg;base64,"},"images":{"fallback":{"src":"/static/11814d54ba526a7f1a091b3a262105c2/e737e/auto-news-snapshot.jpg","srcSet":"/static/11814d54ba526a7f1a091b3a262105c2/e737e/auto-news-snapshot.jpg 800w","sizes":"800px"},"sources":[{"srcSet":"/static/11814d54ba526a7f1a091b3a262105c2/e7773/auto-news-snapshot.webp 800w","type":"image/webp","sizes":"800px"}]},"width":800,"height":400}}},"path":"/2017/05/autonews-with-nlp-feature/","date":"2017-05-12T15:06:13.000Z","excerpt":"【新闻源监控系统】发布了0.3.1版本，作为技术探索性项目，本次更新在0.2.0的基础上，增加如下新特性： 爬 … ","title":"【新闻源监控系统】具备了自然语言处理特性","content":"<p>【<a href=\"http://autonews.berlinchan.com\">新闻源监控系统</a>】发布了0.3.1版本，作为技术探索性项目，本次更新在0.2.0的基础上，增加如下新特性：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>爬虫与 API 部署到 docker 容器中</li>\n<li>系统具有了人工智能 NLP 特性，包括关键字提取、新闻分类、情感评价。模型都采用 NLP 工具现成的，在情感评价和新闻分类上的准确率还有待提高。</li>\n<li>关键字提取使用 <a href=\"https://github.com/hankcs/HanLP\">HanLP</a></li>\n<li>新闻分类使用 <a href=\"http://thuctc.thunlp.org/\">THUCTC</a></li>\n<li>情感评价使用&nbsp;<a href=\"https://github.com/isnowfy/snownlp\">SnowNLP</a></li>\n<li>移植爬虫到 python scrapy 框架下</li>\n</ul>\n<p>顺着新闻分类的开发，看了一下朴素贝叶斯算法，不过还需要先复习复习线性代数。</p>\n<p>文章《<a href=\"http://m.leiphone.com/news/201705/6B4Bi97UEDgOjR1Z.html?viewType=weixin\">我是如何用机器学习技术帮助 HR 省时间的</a>》中，提到的三种机器学习的文本分类算法： TextGrocery，fastText，Naive Bayes都值得一一细看一下。</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/2017/05/autonews-with-nlp-feature/"}},"